Investment Management





Thank you for contacting Brown Brothers Harriman.
      









    Investment Management
  


Brown Brothers Harriman Investment Management's mission is to strive to protect and grow our clients' capital over meaningful periods of time; and our strategy is to focus on scalable investment strategies where our philosophy, approach, and expertise can lead to differentiated results.  BBH Investment Management has been managing equity and fixed income investments for over 80 years and our unique investment approach is what sets us apart.Our approach to investing is guided by a set of core principles that are applied across the full breadth of our investment portfolio. Together they amount to a time-tested philosophy that has built lasting client relationships and set us apart from our peers.Our investment principles:focus on capital preservationvalue-based approachbottom-up fundamental researchlong-term perspectivediscipline and patience









          Public Equity
        

Brown Brothers Harriman’s public equity strategies seek to generate attractive long-term investment returns over full market cycles with an emphasis on capital preservation.


U.S. Large Cap Equity
Global Equity


U.S. Small & Mid-Cap Equity







          Fixed Income
        

We offer taxable, tax-exempt, and inflation-indexed strategies that utilize our unique investment philosophy and valuation methodology that seeks to generate long-term, peer-leading returns.


Taxable Fixed Income Strategies
Tax-Exempt Fixed income Strategy


U.S. TIPS Strategy









          Mutual Funds
        

Brown Brothers Harriman mutual funds share a value-based investment philosophy grounded in bottom-up, fundamentally-derived research.


Learn more











NOT FDIC INSURED   NO BANK GUARANTEE   MAY LOSE VALUE



























 











