Investor Services





Thank you for contacting Brown Brothers Harriman.
      









    Investor Services
  


Brown Brothers Harriman Investor Services provides asset servicing and technology solutions to leading global asset gatherers. We focus on a select number of clients seeking a highly engaged partner to give them a competitive edge. Each client receives a highly personalized and bespoke service combined with superior technology.As a privately held company without the distraction of third party shareholders, BBH can be wholly focused on our clients. We work with them on what matters most to help differentiate their businesses and achieve their growth objectives.Clients look to BBH to uncover value, find better ways to manage risk and complexity, and grow their businesses. They expect measurably superior service, and we deliver. Clients have described us as their first call when they need to figure out the new and difficult. They routinely rank BBH their top global service provider.









          Custody & Fund Services
        

Ensuring the accurate trade settlement, safekeeping, reporting and administration of our clients’ most complex funds and asset types


Custody
Depositary & Trustee
Fund Accounting
Fund Administration


Transfer Agency
Global Tax
Collateral Management
Fund Order & Custody







          Specialist Expertise
        

Providing specialist expertise servicing cross-border funds, alternatives, ETFs, and insurance firms.  Our regulatory intelligence enhances our expertise in these areas, keeping clients informed of markets and requirements impacting their businesses


Cross-Border Funds
US Funds
Distribution Intelligence
Alternative Funds


Exchange Traded Funds
Insurance
Regulatory Intelligence









          Markets
        

Providing foreign exchange trading, currency administration, and securities lending solutions centered on execution quality and leading levels of operational efficiency, transparency, and client control


Foreign Exchange
Active FX Execution
InfoFX


Currency Hedging
Securities Lending
Market Intelligence







          Investment Operations & Technology Solutions
        

Making key components of our technology platform available to clients on a SaaS, IaaS, and fully outsourced basis


Technology Services


